## 6) Ops/Admin Workflow (Manual Approval v1)

### 6.1 Provider Review Queue
Admin sees:
- Applicant summary
- Zone/category requested
- BYOC estimate
- Compliance checklist (license/insurance uploaded or not)
- Risk flags (missing docs, category mismatch)
- Agreement acceptance audit log
Actions:
- Approve
- Approve with conditions (e.g., “no courtesy upgrade”)
- Waitlist
- Reject (with reason template)

### 6.2 Post-approval activation
When approved:
- Provider gets a “Welcome — you’re approved” screen
- Next steps:
  - “Complete your first test job” (optional)
  - “Invite BYOC customers” (script + link)
  - “Set availability” (if missing)

### 6.3 Ops-configurable controls
- Enable/disable categories in zone
- Cap number of providers per category
- Founding Partner slots remaining counter
- Incentive plan assignment

