## 7) Messaging Logic (Opportunity banners)
Implement a deterministic copy engine:

Inputs:
- provider ZIP → mapped zone
- categories selected
- `market_zone_category_state` (OPEN / WAITLIST / CLOSED / EARLY)
- number of existing providers in that category in that zone
- founding partner slot availability

Outputs:
- Banner variant A/B/C/D/E
- CTA label: Apply / Join waitlist / Not accepting

