## 8) Data Model (Suggested)

### `provider_applications`
- id
- provider_user_id
- provider_org_id (nullable)
- status (DRAFT, SUBMITTED, UNDER_REVIEW, APPROVED, WAITLISTED, REJECTED)
- requested_zones (array)
- requested_categories (array)
- byoc_estimate_json
- compliance_json (license, insurance, background_check)
- submitted_at, reviewed_at, decision_reason

### `provider_agreement_acceptance`
- id
- provider_application_id
- clause_key
- accepted_at
- ip_address (optional)
- device_id (optional)

### `provider_compliance_documents`
- id
- provider_org_id
- doc_type (COI, license_proof, etc.)
- storage_url
- expires_at (for insurance)
- verified_by_admin_id
- verified_at
- status (UPLOADED, VERIFIED, REJECTED)

### `provider_onboarding_events` (analytics)
- event_type, timestamp, payload

